name: Expand Your Circle
body:
### What is Expand Your Circle?
This app can be used by people of all ages to learn about birds in the local area of northern Illinois. This app is used for informational purposes for people who have an interest in wildlife. You will be able to scroll through a variety of birds to get information about them such as an image, habitat, food, etc.
